OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,FSaturday evening with isolated
OL,7,Fthundery showers clearing. Cloud
OL,8,Fincreasing to bring a few showers from
OL,9,Fthe west overnight, mostly to the
OL,10,FPennines. Eastern areas remaining
OL,11,Fmostly dry. Temperatures remaining
OL,12,Fwarm overnight. Winds southwesterly
OL,13,Fand mostly light.
OL,14,
OL,15,CSunday:FFresher conditions spreading
OL,16,Fto all parts into Sunday, with
OL,17,Fsunshine and possible showers. More
OL,18,Fseasonable temperatures than expected.
OL,19,FWinds moderate southwesterly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
